Command: evolve [Other shortcut names: Evo]
Evolves your card into different evolutions! Takes 2 copies of the same card as well as a gold cost (both have to be at MAX LVL) and combines it to evolve it. -> .evolve <card #> <card material # or empty, bot will search for the first material it can find for you>
Use ahelp <command or command group, case sensitive> for more info on a command.

AniGame BOT 22-Jul-20 05:16 PM
Command: team
Battle team actions. Views your selected battle team is no other command is used alongside it.
team create [name]
Creates your battle team! Note that you can only have 5 teams created at once.
team delete <team>
Deletes your battle team!
team select <team>
Switches and selects your battle team!
team set <card_num>
Assigns your familiar to a battle team!
team view [team]
Views your battle team! If you don't have a name selected, it will show all of your teams.
Use ahelp <command or command group, case sensitive> for more info on a command.
